It is! It's a table. The table is massive. On the table you can make out a cookbook. Classic TextWorld. You see a gleam over in a corner, where you can see a counter. The counter is vast. On the counter you can see a knife. You can make out a stove. The stove is conventional. But the thing is empty, unfortunately.
